    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "On April 17, 1960, a lecture was given by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "at Phipps Auditorium, City Park, Denver,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Colorado, which was advertised to be a lecture, movie film,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "and discussion of unidentified flying objects. The audience",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "was comprised of a majority of older individuals and also",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "a majority of the audience was female. There were few",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "young people, although some family groups.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "The program was sponsored by the Denver [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED], one of which",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "meets monthly at the [REDACTED], Lakewood,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Colorado, whose [REDACTED] was the Master of Ceremonies.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "The program consisted of a 45 minute movie which included",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "several shots of things purported to be flying saucers, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "then a number of interviews with people from all walks of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "life regarding sightings they had made of such unidentified",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "flying objects. After the movie [REDACTED] gave a",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "lecture which was more of a religious-economics lecture",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "rather than one of unidentified flying objects.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that he had been in the \"flying",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "game\" for over 30 years and currently operates a private",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Civil Aeronautics Authority approved airfield in California.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "He said he has personally observed a good many sightings and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "has talked to hundreds of people who have also seen flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "saucers. He said that he has also been visited by the people",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "from outer space and has taken up the cause of bringing the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "facts of these people to the American people. He said it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "is a crusade which he has undertaken because he is more or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "less retired, his family is grown and gone from home, and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "he feels he might be doing some good by this work.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "PROPERTY OF FBI - This memorandum is loaned to you by the",
